43 special accounts therein as may be determined by the State Treasurer and shall
44 be disbursed as provided in this section. Monies in the Education Bonds Fund
45 shall be allocated and expended as provided in this section.
46 Any additional monies that may be received by means of a grant or grants
47 from the United States of America or any agency or department thereof or
48 from any other source for deposit to the Education Bonds Fund may be placed
