4 (1) The amount of funds requested by each school.
5 (2) The purposes of funds requested by each school.
6 (3) The amount of funds allocated to each school.
7 (4) The use of funds allocated to each school.
8 (5) Any effects of the model on school outcomes, including attendance rates,
