5 SECTION 7.3.(a) Purpose of the College Advising Corps Program. – From the funds
6 appropriated in subsection (b) of this section, the Board of Governors of The University of North
7 Carolina shall make funds available to the National College Advising Corps, Inc., (CAC) to
